### TABLEDATA

CREATE TABLE website_traffic ( 
  id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
  visitor_id INT, 
  page_id INT, 
  timestamp TIMESTAMP, 
  traffic_source VARCHAR(100) 
);

CREATE TABLE conversion_rates ( 
  id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
  page_id INT, 
  conversion_id INT, 
  conversion_rate DECIMAL(5, 2), 
  timestamp TIMESTAMP 
);

### STATEMENT

DELETE FROM website_traffic WHERE id = 1;
